Name: Dead Tunnel
About the game: Dead Tunnel is 2D Shooter Platformer Roguelite game. Players must venture into a secret tunnel where monsters await. Players have to buy weapons at the end of the stage to create a variety of battles. Players must upgrade their character's abilities to become stronger in order to fight the boss.
